Package: EnsDb.Gmax.Wm82.v62
Title: Ensembl-based annotations for Glycine max (soybean) assembly Williams 82 v4
Description: This package provides gene, transcript and exon annotations for the
    soybean genome assembly Williams 82 v4 (Glycine_max_v2.1), based on
    Ensembl Plants release 62.  Gene IDs follow the Wm82.a4.v1 nomenclature
    (Glyma.XXGXXXXXX).  Chromosome lengths are included.
Version: 0.99.0
